properties.name: allowsVOIP
properties.docs: iOS only: If this carrier allows VOIP calls to be made on its network.

properties.name: carrierName
properties.docs: The name of the cellular service provider.

properties.name: isoCountryCode
properties.docs:
Country code for the cellular service provider,
represented as an ISO 3166-1 country code string.

properties.name: mobileCountryCode
properties.docs:
Mobile country code (MCC) for the cellular service provider,
in its numeric representation.

properties.name: mobileNetworkCode
properties.docs:
Mobile network code (MNC) for the cellular service provider,
in its numeric representation.
